 25 June COVID-19 statistics in South Africa. The number of new cases is 18 762 and the cumulative cases is 1 895 905. Number of deaths is 215 which brings the total to 59 621. Total number of recoveries is 1 690 380. The recovery rate is 89.2%. Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Republic of South Africa, Department of Health. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .